{
  "stem": "4710.4",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my wife is working very hard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She's got her own business, and she's really doing very well in property management.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, very difficult.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm not being a-- I'm not being a-- an ideologist, just an ordinary person.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All, all what I can tell them, we are very, very staunch to our religion.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And with all the difficulties, we have managed-- I feel is everybody who survived is a victory over Nazism, over Hitler, is a victory for the Jewish nation, and for the Jewish faith.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if-- if we-- if we don't keep to our faith, then end of the day, is the victor is again, Hitler, and not us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this is very important.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I tried to bring them up, the children, they should be loyal to-- to the Jewish beliefs and practice.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And thank God, I'm very successful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Children are all wonderful children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Quite honestly, while I was in Auschwitz, the only way you could survive that you don't think of faith, and God, and anything.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Don't think of anything spiritual.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just think of yourself as an animal and whose duty is not to be taken to the slaughterhouse, and to get as much food as you can.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And don't think about this thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you start thinking about it, then you-- then you are lost.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If you're looking around what happens here to us, then the conclusion would be not favorable for survival.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I was-- I made a conscious effort at that time, which I think it was the right decision, not to think of anything spiritual.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Though occasionally when I felt desperate, I prayed to God to help me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But I was-- I was not-- I never had any doubts in God that he is going to help us.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
